<!-- ABOUT -->
<section id="about" class="about">

<img src=https://media.istockphoto.com/id/1330249432/vector/electric-car-it-charging-a-battery-an-electric-recharge-station-ecology-concept-eco-city.jpg?s=612x612&w=0&k=20&c=APzO7FHsIIrUG0NCirpUS10cDn6XvGEr9fnP_rFDfcc=>

<div class="about-content">
<h2>EV-OPTIMA Start is a complete analytics tool for electric vehicles all over the world</h2>

<p>
Electric Vehicles are transforming transportation with clean energy solutions.EV-OPTIMA monitors battery performance, charging efficiency, range optimization,
and global EV adoption trends. It helps governments, businesses and researchers
make data-driven decisions for sustainable mobility.
</p>

<div id="moreText" style="display:none;">
    <p>
As EV adoption grows worldwide, the need for accurate data and performance insights becomes essential. EV-OPTIMA Start serves as a complete analytics tool that monitors and analyzes electric vehicle trends across different countries and markets. It provides valuable insights into battery performance, driving range, charging infrastructure, and market growth.

By collecting worldwide data, the platform helps users compare EV performance and identify emerging opportunities. EV-OPTIMA Start supports governments and businesses in making data-driven decisions for sustainable mobility planning. It also helps researchers and students understand global EV adoption patterns.

Through interactive dashboards and real-time analytics, it transforms complex information into clear visual insights. Overall, EV-OPTIMA Start strengthens worldwide electric mobility by connecting innovation, data, and sustainability.

    </p>
</div>

<button class="btn" onclick="toggleReadMore()" id="readBtn">
    Read More
</button>

</div>
